10- How to achieve character and voice consistency
When creating long videos, character and voice consistency is key. Follow these steps to maintain the best level of coherence throughout your scenes:

Create a detailed character description: Your description is the foundation for consistency. To ensure reusability and voice consistency, build out the description for your character with a rich set of unchangeable features: physical build and age, hair color and style, facial structure, eye color and shape, any defining marks and a voice style. You can use Gemini to generate an exhaustive verbal description of your characterâ€™s facial features.
Apply the description consistently: Copy and paste the entire, unchanged character description into your prompt for every new scene. Only modify the parts that describe the new action or setting. To speed up your workflow, you can also use Gemini as a scene generator. Provide it with your final character description and ask it to generate multiple scene prompts for you.
Use the same seed parameter: Seed numbers are numerical values that control the randomness in the AIâ€™s generation process. Using the same seed with the same prompt will likely generate very similar outputs, while altering the seed can lead to variations. For specific details on how to integrate the seed parameter, refer to the VEO API specification.
Example: Character and voice consistency

1ï¸âƒ£Prompt for Scene 1: â€œA medium shot, with the camera slowly dollying forward in a dimly lit, grand Parisian archive. Dust motes dance in a single beam of light from a high window. Clara, a historian in her early 30s, with observant, dark brown eyes that hold a quiet intensity. She has chin-length, black hair styled in a classic bob. She is dressed in a sophisticated, dark navy-blue wool coat, with a silk scarf patterned with subtle gold and cream designs tied around her neck. She stands before a large, ancient wooden table, carefully turning the fragile, yellowed page of a massive, leather-bound book. Her expression is one of deep concentration. In a voice that is crisp and clear, with a thoughtful, analytical tone and a standard american accent, Clara says: It has to be hereâ€ 2ï¸âƒ£Prompt for Scene 2: â€A wide shot of the Pont des Arts in Paris at twilight, the sky a mix of deep blue and soft orange. The lights of the city are beginning to twinkle on along the Seine. Clara, a historian in her early 30s, with observant, dark brown eyes that hold a quiet intensity. She has chin-length, black hair styled in a classic bob. She is dressed in a sophisticated, dark navy-blue wool coat, with a silk scarf patterned with subtle gold and cream designs tied around her neck. She leans against the railing, looking out at the water, a small, triumphant smile on her face. She pulls a folded, old map from her coat pocket and looks down at it. In a voice that is crisp and clear, with a thoughtful, analytical tone and a standard american accent, Clara says: I knew it. The path starts from hereâ€ 3ï¸âƒ£Prompt for Scene 3: â€œAn eye-level shot in a small, hidden Parisian courtyard, overgrown with ivy and lit by a single, warm gas lamp. Clara, a historian in her early 30s, with observant, dark brown eyes that hold a quiet intensity. She has chin-length, black hair styled in a classic bob. She is dressed in a sophisticated, dark navy-blue wool coat, with a silk scarf patterned with subtle gold and cream designs tied around her neck. She kneels down and runs her fingers over an ancient, carved symbol on a stone paver, almost completely obscured by moss. Her eyes light up with discovery. In a voice that is crisp and clear, with a thoughtful, analytical tone and a standard american accent, Clara says: After all these years, Iâ€™ve found itâ€
Conclusion
This guide shares experimentation-based best practices for structuring prompts, helping you create compelling videos with Veo 3 and bring your creative concepts to life.

As you create, keep in mind that Veo applies safety filters across Vertex AI to help ensure that generated videos and uploaded photos donâ€™t contain offensive content. For example, prompts that violate responsible AI guidelines are blocked.

